<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h3>안녕하세요 <%= @message.recipients.first.first_name %>님</h3>
    
    
    <p><b><%= @message.sender.first_name.capitalize %></b>으로부터 새로운 메세지가 도착했습니다.</p>
    <blockquote>
      <p style="border-left: 3px solid #0068C0; padding-left: 12px;">
        <%= @subject %><br><br>
        <%= raw @message.body %><br>
        <span style="color:#757582">Sent on <%= @message.conversation.updated_at.strftime("%m/%e/%Y %I:%M %p") %></span>
      </p>
    </blockquote>
    <br>
    <br>
    <p>
      <%= link_to "답장하기", conversation_url(:id => @message.conversation.id), :style => "background-color: #0068C0;
    -moz-border-radius: 5px;
    -webkit-border-radius: 5px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 20px;
    padding: 7px 10px 7px 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    border:none;" %>
    </p>
    
   </body>
</html>
